Package mars

Class ErrorList

java.lang.Object
mars.ErrorList
public class ErrorList extends Object
Maintains list of generated error messages, regardless of source (tokenizing, parsing, assembly, execution).
Version:
August 2003
Author:
Pete Sanderson
